      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('2-2',1,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">B</span>The chip creates a unique one-time code for every payment, so stolen data can't be reused</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('2-2',2,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>The chip is encrypted with your fingerprint</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('2-2',3,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">D</span>The chip doesn't store any card information at all</button>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-feedback" id="qfb-2-2"></div>
