      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('3-1',2,2)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>Online, the fraudster only needs the card number and expiry — they don't have to be physically present with the card or know the PIN</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('3-1',3,2)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">D</span>Banks don't monitor online transactions</button>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-feedback" id="qfb-3-1"></div>
