      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('3-2',1,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">B</span>Hang up immediately — real banks never ask for your OTP. Call your bank back on the number on their website.</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('3-2',2,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>Give them the last 3 digits only</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('3-2',3,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">D</span>Ask them to send you a confirmation email first, then share the code</button>
    </div>
