      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('6-1',1,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">B</span>Challenge — the unfamiliar country and IP are high-risk signals your bank will want to verify</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('6-1',2,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>Declined automatically — banks block all overseas online transactions</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('6-1',3,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">D</span>Frictionless — 3DS only applies to domestic transactions</button>
    </div>
