      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('10-1',1,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">B</span>Premium travel cards have higher interchange rates — the restaurant effectively subsidises the cardholder's air miles through the higher merchant fee</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('10-1',2,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>Premium cards are more likely to be fraudulent so merchants pay a risk premium</button>
      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('10-1',3,1)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">D</span>Premium cardholders tend to spend more so are charged at a higher percentage</button>
