      <button class="quiz-opt" onclick="answer('15-1',2,2)"><span class="quiz-opt-letter">C</span>Entry into Visa's VDMP (ratio above 0.65%) and/or Mastercard's ECP (above 1%) — with escalating monthly fines if the ratio doesn't improve</button>
